extends EnemyBullet
    An EmbeddedBullet is an EnemyBullet that shoots out other bullets (in patterns, of course).

    bowenzhi

        Parameters:
        velocity - speed of bullet
        acceleration - acceleration of bullet
        airFric - air friction of bullet
        hitbox - hitbox of bullet
        sprite - sprite of bullet
        spriteSize - sprite size of bullet
        vulnerableHitbox - hitbox of bullet that the bullet can be hit on
        hp - durability of bullet
        lockAngle - determines whether or not to calculate the angle the bullet is moving in for sprite animations
        embeddedPattern - pattern that this bullet shoots other bullets out with
        frequency - frequency that this bullet shoots other bullets out with
        oscillator - Oscillator for shooting varying the pattern that the bullets are shot out with
